pullRequest.title: Link directly to Presto connector  doc
pullRequest.bodyText:
At @blue's suggestion, this PR changes site/mkdocs.yml to link directly
to the Presto connector documentation.  On @electrum's advice,  it leaves
docs/presto.md in place, in case folks link to it directly.

commit.message:
Link directly to Presto connector  doc

At @blue's suggestion, this PR changes stie/mkdocs.yml to link directly
to the Presto connector documentation.  On @electrum's advice,  it leaves
docs/presto.md in place, in case folks link to it directly.

nodes.bodyText: Now there are no links to "presto.md". We probably should remove it
